'''"Lignyot"''' was what members of the [[Senate Bureau of Intelligence/Legends|SBI]] for the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]], and, later, [[Imperial Intelligence/Legends|Imperial Intelligence's]] Cryptoanalysis Branch of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] called themselves. It was not believed that the term had any actual meaning.

